title: Crimson Force
description:
Synopsis

C. Thomas Howell (SOUL MAN) stars in this sci-fi thriller about a mission to Mars that goes horribly wrong. A crew from Earth has been despatched to the red planet to mine some precious resources, but when they arrive they discover that the planet is populated with angry Martians who are at war with one another.


Cast & Crew

Actors: 	C. Thomas Howell, David Chokachi, Jeff Fahey, Steven Williams, Julia Rose
